{"tid":1219301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依首詩歌幾適合做戰歌","createTime":"2019-06-13T19:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T01:35:45.000Z","uid":93450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c81bf23078f87027171f6b6ea750dc64f2cd233b","tid":1219301,"uid":93450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:07:13.000Z","msg":"頭先喺隔離post見到<br />\n聽落幾有氣勢 用鼓打出黎應該都幾有feel<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AhE9VhSxvh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAhE9VhSxvh4&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=6487dee5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AhE9VhSxvh4</a>"},{"pid":"02594f8aada289f71d8a55ca88211bc8ac3b0158","tid":1219301,"uid":93450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:22:26.000Z","msg":"去唱聖詩嘅基督徒可以考慮下依首<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d57ae4998457a9ca0b45d0ce22ec320246325b","tid":1219301,"uid":93450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3924090f5e0ccba68bbd60bdf44a483e20329cc9","tid":1219301,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"聖經好有意思重覆睇幾次，再埋近日既事我節錄左少少，希望有巴打可以加D圖<br />\n再去金鐘佈道講經解釋比其他人知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申命記 28:50 這民的面貌兇惡，不顧恤年老的，也不恩待年少的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申命記 17:13 眾百姓都要聽見害怕，不再擅敢行事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申命記 22:18 本城的長老要拿住那人，懲治他<br />\n<br />\n申命記17：5<br />\n你就要將行這惡事的男人或女人拉到城門外，用石頭將他打死。<br />\n<br />\n申命記 23:9 「你出兵攻打仇敵，就要遠避諸惡」<br />\n<br />\n申命記 20:2 你們將要上陣的時候，祭司要到百姓面前宣告<br />\n<br />\n申命記 19:21 你眼不可顧惜，要以命償命，以眼還眼，以牙還牙，以手還手，以腳還腳。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n申命記 19:20 別人聽見都要害怕，就不敢在你們中間再行這樣的惡了。<br />\n<br />\n申命記 20:9 官長對百姓宣告完了，就當派軍長率領他們。<br />\n<br />\n申命記 32:23 我要將禍患堆在他們身上，把我的箭向他們射盡。<br />\n<br />\n申命記 21:21 本城的眾人就要用石頭將他打死。這樣，就把那惡從你們中間除掉，以色列眾人都要聽見害怕。」<br />\n<br />\n申命記 20:12 若不肯與你和好，反要與你打仗，你就要圍困那城。<br />\n<br />\n出埃及記 15:7\t你大發威嚴、推翻那些起來攻擊你的、你發出烈怒如火、燒滅他們像燒碎一樣。<br />\n<br />\n記得唔好咁快放棄<br />\n<br />\n申命記 32:31 據我們的仇敵自己斷定，他們的磐石不如我們的磐石。<br />\n<br />\n有人比人捉記得救人<br />\n<br />\n申命記 24:7 「若遇見人拐帶以色列中的一個弟兄，當奴才待他，或是賣了他，那拐帶人的就必治死。這樣，便將 那惡從你們中間除掉。<br />\n<br />\n致廢老，愛國愛黨人士<br />\n<br />\n申命記 32:29 惟願他們有智慧，能明白這事，肯思念他們的結局。<br />\n<br />\n最後致天價賣生理鹽水既藥坊<br />\n<br />\n申命記 23:19 你借給你弟兄的，或是錢財或是糧食，無論什麼可生利的物，都不可取利。"},{"pid":"708484e3846b717209b4c1ed863a42ffa40a81c9","tid":1219301,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:08:39.000Z","msg":"主能夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9_tIPgNjBS0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9_tIPgNjBS0&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=a8ad1ce6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9_tIPgNjBS0</a>"},{"pid":"d1931add0da6c73623ed7736e5c83e751c60928f","tid":1219301,"uid":93450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"708484e3846b717209b4c1ed863a42ffa40a81c9","tid":1219301,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:08:39.000Z","msg":"主能夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9_tIPgNjBS0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9_tIPgNjBS0&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=a8ad1ce6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9_tIPgNjBS0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:32:31.000Z","msg":"主能夠玩野味太濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08e038bbd1f4c41e457eb8c0a2b729751984c95","tid":1219301,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:35:45.000Z","msg":"細路仔嘅可以用呢首<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yZobCx3fY0o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyZobCx3fY0o&d=